sources.title: Secrets of a Model (1940) SEEDY MELODRAMA
sources.description:
PizzaFLIX Presents CLASSIC MOVIE MONDAY
Producer:  J.D Kendis
Stars: Cheryl Walker/Sharon Lee, Harold Daniels, Julian Madison

Cheryl Walker used the alias "Sharon Lee" for her first starring role as a struggling carhop who takes a stroll on the seedy side to pay for her mother's life-saving operation. This cautionary tale from Exploitation producer J.D Kendis promised "A lesson for every girl and a warning for every parent.‚Äù  

TRIVIA: Out of 1,500 beautiful schoolgirls, Cheryl Walker was crowned "Rose Queen" for the 1938 Pasadena Tournament of Roses.

metadata.Plot: A carhop in need of money for her dying mother's operation poses for a sculpture. Later, she gets involved with drunken playboys and winds up pregnant.
metadata.Writer: Sherman L. Lowe, Arthur St. Claire
metadata.Actors: Cheryl Walker, Harold Daniels, Julian Madison
